zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2530815\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2530815\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Aug 14, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ozf1665702734970.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ozf1665702734970.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ozf1665702734970.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ozf1665702734970\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      keyword\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Adds double quotes around field and table names and sets the Sybase option <code class=\"ph codeph\">quoted_identifier</code> on.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"ozf1665702734970__topic_d59594e1_d59595e1_d59596e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ozf1665702734970__p_d59597e1_d59598e1_d59599e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">USYS$SYB_PARAMS</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">= keyword</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ozf1665702734970__section_tth_lqw_jcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d390410e66\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ozf1665702734970__p_d59603e1_d59604e1_d59605e1\">Specify the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">keyword</span> option if you\n            need to:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"ozf1665702734970__ul_lf1_mqw_jcc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ozf1665702734970__li_d26657e1_d26658e1_d26659e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ozf1665702734970__p_d59606e1_d59607e1_d59608e1\">Use Sybase reserved words in field and table\n                  names. This is required if the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">sql</span> ProcScript statement is used\n                  with double quotes in queries.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ozf1665702734970__li_d26660e1_d26661e1_d26662e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ozf1665702734970__p_d59609e1_d59610e1_d59611e1\">Use Unicode characters in SQL Workbench, the\n                     <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">sql</span> ProcScript statement, and error messages. In this case,\n                  the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">unicode</span> option must be specified as well.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ozf1665702734970__p_d59612e1_d59613e1_d59614e1\">With <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">keyword</span> is specified, strings\n            between single quotes (<code class=\"ph codeph\">'12345'</code>) are treated as data, and strings\n            between double quotes (<code class=\"ph codeph\">\"StreetNameColumn\"</code>) are treated as column\n            names.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ozf1665702734970__p_d59615e1_d59616e1_d59617e1\">For details on the use of the\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">quoted_identifier</code> setting, consult the Sybase documentation.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ozf1665702734970__section_ugp_mqw_jcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d390410e120\">Example: Enabling Unicode Support</h2>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"ozf1665702734970__pre_uyp_nqw_jcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">usys$syb_params charset utf8, unicode, smp, keyword</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tlc1665702735327.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>unicode</a><p>Enable or disable Unicode support in the SYB connector.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530815\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530815\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "keyword Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 14, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 keyword Adds double quotes around field and table names and sets the Sybase option quoted_identifier on. USYS$SYB_PARAMS = keyword Description Specify the keyword option if you need to: Use Sybase reserved words in field and table names. This is required if the sql ProcScript statement is used with double quotes in queries. Use Unicode characters in SQL Workbench, the sql ProcScript statement, and error messages. In this case, the unicode option must be specified as well. With keyword is specified, strings between single quotes ( '12345' ) are treated as data, and strings between double quotes ( \"StreetNameColumn\" ) are treated as column names. For details on the use of the quoted_identifier setting, consult the Sybase documentation. Example: Enabling Unicode Support usys$syb_params charset utf8, unicode, smp, keyword Copy Related Links unicode Enable or disable Unicode support in the SYB connector. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}